cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image saliency detection, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The proposed model uses two neural networks and an adversarial training procedure, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Additionally, the paper introduces a new type of layer, which could be of interest to researchers in neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) fields.
